sh</a></figcaption></img></figure><h3 id="buy-a-gift-item-for-yourself">Buy a gift item for yourself</h3><p>It doesn't matter whether it's one dollar or not. I am generous by buying gifts for other people but not for myself and always try to choose reasonable or the cheapest. Recently I bought an audio for myself as a gift and I feel more happier than before when listening to music.</p><figure class="kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504288041952-91e61c2ebc6e?crop=entropy&#x26;cs=tinysrgb&#x26;fit=max&#x26;fm=jpg&#x26;ixid=MXwxMTc3M3wwfDF8c2VhcmNofDEzN3x8Z2lmdHxlbnwwfHx8&#x26;ixlib=rb-1.2.1&#x26;q=80&#x26;w=2000" class="kg-image" alt="How to improve self-esteem" srcset="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504288041952-91e61c2ebc6e?crop=entropy&#x26;cs=tinysrgb&#x26;fit=max&#x26;fm=jpg&#x26;ixid=MXwxMTc3M3wwfDF8c2VhcmNofDEzN3x8Z2lmdHxlbnwwfHx8&#x26;ixlib=rb-1.2.1&#x26;q=80&#x26;w=600 600w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504288041952-91e61c2ebc6e?crop=entropy&#x26;cs=tinysrgb&#x26;fit=max&#x26;fm=jpg&#x26;ixid=MXwxMTc3M3wwfDF8c2VhcmNofDEzN3x8Z2lmdHxlbnwwfHx8&#x26;ixlib=rb-1.2.1&#x26;q=80&#x26;w=1000 1000w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504288041952-91e61c2ebc6e?crop=entropy&#x26;cs=tinysrgb&#x26;fit=max&#x26;fm=jpg&#x26;ixid=MXwxMTc3M3wwfDF8c2VhcmNofDEzN3x8Z2lmdHxlbnwwfHx8&#x26;ixlib=rb-1.2.1&#x26;q=80&#x26;w=1600 1600w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504288041952-91e61c2ebc6e?crop=entropy&#x26;cs=tinysrgb&#x26;fit=max&#x26;fm=jpg&#x26;ixid=MXwxMTc3M3wwfDF8c2VhcmNofDEzN3x8Z2lmdHxlbnwwfHx8&#x26;ixlib=rb-1.2.1&#x26;q=80&#x26;w=2400 2400w" sizes="(min-width: 720px) 720px"><figcaption>Photo by <a href="https://unsplash.com/@jontyson?utm_source=ghost&#x26;utm_medium=referral&#x26;utm_campaign=api-credit">Jon Tyson</a> / <a href="https://unsplash.com/?utm_source=ghost&#x26;utm_medium=referral&#x26;utm_campaign=api-credit">Unsplash</a></figcaption></img></figure><h3 id="compliment-yourself">Compliment yourself</h3><p>People with low self-esteem say bad things to themselves without hesitation. Don't forget that these words can hurt yourself.</p><figure class="kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585816805044-f8179ae1e5e0?crop=entropy&#x26;cs=tinysrgb&#x26;fit=max&#x26;fm=jpg&#x26;ixid=MXwxMTc3M3wwfDF8c2VhcmNofDMzfHxjaGVlciUyMHVwfGVufDB8fHw&#x26;ixlib=rb-1.2.1&#x26;q=80&#x26;w=2000" class="kg-image" alt="How to improve self-esteem" srcset="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585816805044-f8179ae1e5e0?crop=entropy&#x26;cs=tinysrgb&#x26;fit=max&#x26;fm=jpg&#x26;ixid=MXwxMTc3M3wwfDF8c2VhcmNofDMzfHxjaGVlciUyMHVwfGVufDB8fHw&#x26;ixlib=rb-1.2.1&#x26;q=80&#x26;w=600 600w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585816805044-f8179ae1e5e0?crop=entropy&#x26;cs=tinysrgb&#x26;fit=max&#x26;fm=jpg&#x26;ixid=MXwxMTc3M3wwfDF8c2VhcmNofDMzfHxjaGVlciUyMHVwfGVufDB8fHw&#x26;ixlib=rb-1.2.1&#x26;q=80&#x26;w=1000 1000w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585816805044-f8179ae1e5e0?crop=entropy&#x26;cs=tinysrgb&#x26;fit=max&#x26;fm=jpg&#x26;ixid=MXwxMTc3M3wwfDF8c2VhcmNofDMzfHxjaGVlciUyMHVwfGVufDB8fHw&#x26;ixlib=rb-1.2.1&#x26;q=80&#x26;w=1600 1600w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585816805044-f8179ae1e5e0?crop=entropy&#x26;cs=tinysrgb&#x26;fit=max&#x26;fm=jpg&#x26;ixid=MXwxMTc3M3wwfDF8c2VhcmNofDMzfHxjaGVlciUyMHVwfGVufDB8fHw&#x26;ixlib=rb-1.2.1&#x26;q=80&#x26;w=2400 2400w" sizes="(min-width: 720px) 720px"><figcaption>Photo by <a href="https://unsplash.com/@enginakyurt?utm_source=ghost&#x26;utm_medium=referral&#x26;utm_campaign=api-credit">engin akyurt</a> / <a href="https://unsplash.com/?utm_source=ghost&#x26;utm_medium=referral&#x26;utm_campaign=api-credit">Unsplash</a></figcaption></img></figure><h3 id="make-your-favorite-time-and-place">Make your favorite time and place</h3><p>The fact that self-esteem has decreased can be seen as a burden of mind that is difficult for the person to bear. So, making your favorite time and place where you can reflash yourself is a real rest.</p><figure class="kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517699418036-fb5d179fef0c?crop=entropy&#x26;cs=tinysrgb&#x26;fit=max&#x26;fm=jpg&#x26;ixid=MXwxMTc3M3wwfDF8c2VhcmNofDV8fHN1cmZpbmd8ZW58MHx8fA&#x26;ixlib=rb-1.2.1&#x26;q=80&#x26;w=2000" class="kg-image" alt="How to improve self-esteem" srcset="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517699418036-fb5d179fef0c?crop=entropy&#x26;cs=tinysrgb&#x26;fit=max&#x26;fm=jpg&#x26;ixid=MXwxMTc3M3wwfDF8c2VhcmNofDV8fHN1cmZpbmd8ZW58MHx8fA&#x26;ixlib=rb-1.2.1&#x26;q=80&#x26;w=600 600w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517699418036-fb5d179fef0c?crop=entropy&#x26;cs=tinysrgb&#x26;fit=max&#x26;fm=jpg&#x26;ixid=MXwxMTc3M3wwfDF8c2VhcmNofDV8fHN1cmZpbmd8ZW58MHx8fA&#x26;ixlib=rb-1.2.1&#x26;q=80&#x26;w=1000 1000w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517699418036-fb5d179fef0c?crop=entropy&#x26;cs=tinysrgb&#x26;fit=max&#x26;fm=jpg&#x26;ixid=MXwxMTc3M3wwfDF8c2VhcmNofDV8fHN1cmZpbmd8ZW58MHx8fA&#x26;ixlib=rb-1.2.1&#x26;q=80&#x26;w=1600 1600w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517699418036-fb5d179fef0c?crop=entropy&#x26;cs=tinysrgb&#x26;fit=max&#x26;fm=jpg&#x26;ixid=MXwxMTc3M3wwfDF8c2VhcmNofDV8fHN1cmZpbmd8ZW58MHx8fA&#x26;ixlib=rb-1.2.1&#x26;q=80&#x26;w=2400 2400w" sizes="(min-width: 720px) 720px"><figcaption>Photo by <a href="https://unsplash.com/@sachaverheij?utm_source=ghost&#x26;utm_medium=referral&#x26;utm_campaign=api-credit">Sacha Verheij</a> / <a href="https://unsplash.com/?utm_source=ghost&#x26;utm_medium=referral&#x26;utm_campaign=api-credit">Unsplash</a></figcaption></img></figure><h3 id="make-action-plans-you-want">Make action plans you want</h3><p>Let's make a very easy acttion plan you want such as dog walking, take a walk for 5 minutes. A sense of accomplishment and rewards for me can be achieved through such a plan.</p><figure class="kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1599406580992-46ab5d96f296?crop=entropy&#x2